<p>All children applying for the  Saturday School program at DSK International must have a sufficient language proficiency for their age level to join the specific program.</p>

<p class="lead font-weight-bold">English</p>
<p>Students are required to apply and attend an interview for enrollment. Interviews are offered in July and January.</p>

<p class="lead font-weight-bold">German & French</p>
<p>Students are required to apply and attend a trial day. Following a successful trial day, students can be enrolled full time.</p>
